---
title: "US56 — Manage user accounts / roles / access"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as System Admin
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>UsersScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>SetUserStatus
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>Profile
  A->>B: open a user account
  B->>C: suspend(userId) / setRole(...)
  C->>E: Profile status / role change
  note right of E: DB trigger - only admins<br/>may change role or status
  E-->>C: updated
  C-->>B: done
  B-->>A: user suspended / role changed
  note over E: persisted via ProfileGateway → Supabase
